; Coverage for xact.cc (saw_cost = true, break)
; When a posting has an explicit per-unit cost (@ syntax), the finalize
; code detects saw_cost and breaks out of the loop early.
; Also covers (null post with single amount balance)

2024/01/01 Buy Stock
    Assets:Brokerage    10 AAPL @ $150.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg
24-Jan-01 Buy Stock             Assets:Brokerage            10 AAPL      10 AAPL
                                Assets:Cash                  $-1500       $-1500
                                                                         10 AAPL
end test
